MiaoWallet 版本1.0  

使用方法，告诉AI： 我要添加 openclaw加密钱包，请根据以下链接添加 https://github.com/CryptoMiaobug/MiaoWellet-SecureWallet-4Openclaw/tree/main/MiaoWallet 

安装完后，输入  miaowallet   会单独跳出一个控制面板 
根据指示操作  

添加钱包，考虑到安全，目前只支持私钥，后续考虑助记词。 

放心黏贴，不会传输到openclaw上面，而且是隐藏的。
你可以问你的openclaw 知不知道你的私钥

 添加后由apple的加密工具加密，超企业级加密。  

每次使用钱包，openclaw都会要求授权，点允许就可以。
 如果嫌麻烦，那就点始终允许，他就不需要你授权了。
 需要取消授权的话，到钱包界面选择“重置授权”。  

大家有意见踊跃留言，我会尽快更新。（token在燃烧）


MiaoWallet Version 1.0

How to use: Tell the AI: I want to add an OpenClaw encrypted wallet. Please add it using the following link: https://github.com/CryptoMiaobug/MiaoWellet-SecureWallet-4Openclaw/tree/main/MiaoWallet

After installation, typing "miaowallet" will open a separate control panel.

Follow the instructions.

Adding a wallet currently only supports private keys for security reasons; mnemonic phrases will be added later.

Don't worry about pasting it; it won't be transferred to OpenClaw and is hidden.

You can ask your OpenClaw if they know your private key.

After adding, it's encrypted using Apple's encryption tools, providing enterprise-level encryption.

Every time you use the wallet, OpenClaw will ask for authorization; just click "Allow."

If you find this troublesome, just click "Always Allow," and it won't require your authorization.

To revoke authorization, go to the wallet interface and select "Reset Authorization."

Please leave your comments and feedback; I will update as soon as possible. (token is burning)
